## ðŸ§¾ Ejemplo de Consulta

```sql
SELECT 
    p.Name AS Producto,
    SUM(sod.LineTotal) AS TotalVentas
FROM Sales.SalesOrderDetail sod
JOIN Production.Product p ON sod.ProductID = p.ProductID
GROUP BY p.Name
ORDER BY TotalVentas DESC;
